\c 36
\s Vana vaEsau
\p
\v 1 Ndiwoka marudzi aEsau unova Edhomu:
\v 2 Esau wakatora vakadzi vake kuvakunda veKanani, Adha, mukunda waEroni muHeti, naHoribhama mukunda waAna, mukunda waZibhioni muHivhi,
\v 3 naBhasimati mukunda waIshimaeri hanzvadzi yaNebhayoti.
\v 4 Adha ndokubereka Esau Erifazi; Bhasimati ndokubereka Rueri;
\v 5 Ohori­bhama ndokubereka Jeushi naJarami naKora; ava vanakomana vaEsau, vaakaberekerwa panyika yeKanani.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Esau wakatora vakadzi vake nevanakomana vake nevakunda vake, nemweya yose yeimba yake, nemombe dzake nezvipfuwo zvake zvose, nenhumbi dzake dzose dzaakange awana munyika yeKanani, ndokuenda kune \add imwe \add*nyika achibva pachiso chaJakobho munun'una wake.
\v 7 Nekuti zvipfuwo zvavo zvakange zvakawanda zvokuti vaiva vasingagoni kugara pamwe, uye nyika yeutorwa hwavo yakange isingagoni kuvatakura nekuda kwezvipfuwo zvavo.
\v 8 Esau ndokugara kugomo reSeiri; Esau ndiye Edhomu.
\p
\v 9 Zvino awa marudzi aEsau, baba vevaEdhomu, kugomo reSeiri;
\v 10 awa mazita evanakomana vaEsau, Erifazi mwana­komana waAdha mukadzi waEsau, Rueri mwanakomana waBhasimati mukadzi waEsau.
\v 11 Nevanakomana vaEri­fazi vaiva Temani, Omari, Zefo, naGatamu, naKenazi.
\v 12 Zvino Timuna waiva murongo waErifazi, mwanakomana waEsau; wakaberekera Erifazi muAma­reki; ava vanakomana vaAdha muka­dzi waEsau.
\v 13 Zvino ava vanakomana vaRueri, Nahati naZera, Shama naMiza; ava vanakomana vaBhasimati mukadzi waEsau.
\p
\v 14 Zvino ava madzishe evana vaOhoribhama mu­kunda waAna, mukunda waZibhioni mukadzi waEsau; ndokuberekera Esau Jeushi naJarami naKora.
\p
\v 15 Awa madzishe pakati evana vaEsau: Vanakomana vaErifazi dangwe raEsau: Ishe Temani, ishe Omari, ishe Zefo, ishe Kenazi,
\v 16 ishe Kora, ishe Gatamu, ishe Amareki; awa madzishe aErifazi munyika yeEdhomu; ava vanakomana vaAdha.
\p
\v 17 Uye ava vanakomana vaRueri mwanakomana waEsau: Ishe Nahati, ishe Zera, ishe Shama, ishe Miza; aw madzishe aRueri munyika yeEdhomu; ava vanakomana vaBhasi­mati mukadzi waEsau.
\p
\v 18 Uye ava vanakomana vaOhori­bhama, mukadzi waEsau: Ishe Jeushi, ishe Jarami, ishe Kora; ava madzi­she aOhoribhama, mukunda waAna, mukadzi waEsau.
\v 19 Ava vanakomana vaEsau, uye madzishe avo; unova Edhomu.
\p
\v 20 Ava vanakomana vaSeiri muHori, vagari venyika: Rotani naSho­bharu naZibhioni naAna
\v 21 naDhishoni naEzeri naDhishani; ava madzishe evaHori, vanakomana vaSeiri munyika yeEdhomu.
\p
\v 22 Uye vanakomana vaRotani vaiva Hori naHemani; nehanzvadzi yaRotani aiva Timuna.
\p
\v 23 Uye ava vanakomana vaShobharu: Avhani naManahati naEbhari Shefo naOnamu.
\p
\v 24 Uye ava vanakomana vaZibhioni: Vose Aja naAna; ndiAna akawana matsime emvura inopisa murenje achifudza mbongoro dzaZibhioni baba vake.
\p
\v 25 Uye ava vanakomana vaAna: Dhi­shoni naOhoribhama, mukunda waAna.
\p
\v 26 Ava vanakomana vaDhishoni: Hemudhani naEshibhani naIturani naKerani.
\v 27 Ava vanakomana vaEzeri: Bhirihani naZaavhani naAkani.
\v 28 Ava vanakomana vaDhishani: Uzi naArani.
\p
\v 29 Ava madzishe evaHori: Ishe Rotani, ishe Shobharu, ishe Zibhioni, ishe Ana,
\v 30 she Dhishoni, ishe Ezeri, ishe Dhishani; awa ma­dzishe evaHori, nemarudzi avo munyika yeSeiri.
\p
\v 31 Uye awa madzimambo akatonga munyika yeEdhomu, Mambo asati atonga vana vaIsiraeri:
\v 32 Uye Bhera mwanakomana waBheori wakatonga paEdhomu; uye zita reguta rake rainzi Dhinihabha.
\v 33 Zvino Bhera wakafa, Jobhabhu mwanakomana waZera weBhozara akatonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 34 Jobhabhu ndokufa, Hushamu wenyika yavaTemani akatonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 35 Hushamu ndokufa; Hadhadhi, mwanakomana waBhedhadhi, uya akarova Midhiani kusango reMoabhu, akatonga pachigaro chake; uye zita reguta rake rainzi Avhiti.
\v 36 Hadhadhi ndokufa; Samura weMasereka akatonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 37 Samura ndokufa; Shauri weRehobhoti paRwizi akatonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 38 Shauri ndokufa; Bhaarihanani mwanakomana waAkibhori akatonga pachinzvimbo.
\v 39 Bhaari-Hanani mwanakomana waAkibhori ndokufa, Hadhari akatonga pachinzvimbo chake; uye zita reguta rake rainzi Pau; zita romukadzi wake rainzi Mehetabheri, mukunda waMatiredhi, mukunda waMehazahadhi.
\p
\v 40 Uye awa mazita emadzishe ekwaEsau, nedzimba dzavo, nenzvimbo dzawo, nemazita avo: Ishe Timuna, ishe Arivha, ishe Jeteti;
\v 41 nashe Ohori­bhama, nashe Era, nashe Pinoni;
\v 42 i­she Kenazi, ishe Temani, ishe Mi­bhizari,
\v 43 ishe Magidhieri, ishe Iramu; awa madzishe aEdhomu, maererano nenzvimbo dzavo dzekugara, munyika yenhaka yavo. Ndiye Esau, baba vaEdhomu.
